{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Replace the Landfill Tax with a waste premium",
        "additional_details": "Our countryside and cities are blighted with unsightly and often dangerous waste from fly tipping and general littering. Our local authorities are paying for ineffective cleaning up.\r\n \r\nPlacing a value on the delivery of sorted waste at designated recycling, processing and storage centres could help transform our environment, save our wildlife, keep us safe and save money.",
        "background": "The 1996 introduction of Landfill Tax has had the unintended consequences of incentivising fly tipping.\r\n \r\nWe should replace Landfill Tax with a waste premium rewarding the delivery of separated waste at recycling, processing and storage centres.",
